lead_paragraph: New Inter Milan coach Frank de Boer knows that he has a big job on his hands after the former Ajax Amsterdam manager replaced Roberto Mancini at the Italian club on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Inter Job Won't Be Easy, Says New Coach De Boer
